♪ Calm you and anoint you

37:39.126 --> 37:42.172
♪ Myrrh for your
hot forehead, oh ♪

37:42.216 --> 37:45.480
♪ Then you'll feel
everything's all right ♪

37:45.524 --> 37:47.613
♪ Yes, everything's fine ♪

37:47.656 --> 37:51.921
♪ And it's cool
And the ointment's sweet ♪

37:51.965 --> 37:56.578
♪ For the fire in
Your head and feet ♪

37:56.622 --> 38:00.234
♪ Close your eyes,
Close your eyes and relax ♪

38:00.278 --> 38:02.105
♪ Think of nothing tonight

38:02.149 --> 38:05.935
♪ Everything's all right, yes
Everything's all right ♪

38:05.979 --> 38:10.462
Let me start by saying
I'm sorry you had to walk in
on that, Kev.

38:10.505 --> 38:11.854
Moose and I were trying
to figure out a way

38:11.898 --> 38:13.682
to tell you without
causing a spiral.

38:13.726 --> 38:15.075
My spiraling days are over.

38:15.118 --> 38:16.903
Listen,

38:16.946 --> 38:19.949
I know this may be
impossible, Kev...

38:21.473 --> 38:23.388
But I'd love for us
to be friends.

38:25.172 --> 38:27.217
We are friends, Fangs.

38:27.261 --> 38:30.220
And if you and Moose
make each other happy,
then I'm happy, too.

38:30.264 --> 38:31.961
Seriously.

38:32.005 --> 38:36.096
♪ Everything's all right, yes
Everything's all right ♪

38:36.139 --> 38:38.490
♪ Sleep and I shall
soothe you ♪

38:38.533 --> 38:40.622
♪ Calm you and anoint you

38:40.666 --> 38:43.625
♪ Myrrh for your
hot forehead, oh ♪

38:43.669 --> 38:47.150
♪ Then you'll feel
everything's all right ♪

38:47.194 --> 38:49.022
♪ Yes, everything's fine

38:50.719 --> 38:52.460
We'll be in this together, Jim.

38:52.504 --> 38:54.984
We're both family men,
wife and kids.

38:55.028 --> 38:57.813
And I can hear it
in your voice
that you want this.

38:57.857 --> 39:00.599
So I might pass you on
to the queen of the shop,

39:00.642 --> 39:03.253
and she's gonna tell you
why you deserve it.

39:03.297 --> 39:04.690
Okay?

39:04.733 --> 39:06.692
Hold on.

39:06.735 --> 39:08.911
I think I got him.
He just needs a push.

39:09.956 --> 39:10.870
Say no more.

39:12.437 --> 39:14.003
Mr. Nesper,

39:14.047 --> 39:16.484
I hear you're considering
a promising opportunity,

39:16.528 --> 39:21.359
and I just have to say,
this isn't about what
you're putting down right now.

39:21.402 --> 39:22.882
This is about legacy.

39:22.925 --> 39:25.493
How are you taking care
of yourself and your family

39:25.537 --> 39:27.626
for the rest of your life
and theirs?

39:30.759 --> 39:34.197
We absolutely can
and will do that
for you, Mr. Nesper.

39:34.241 --> 39:37.200
And might I add that
Pearls and Posh is honored

39:37.244 --> 39:39.115
to be doing business with you.

39:42.945 --> 39:43.816
[beeps]

39:45.339 --> 39:49.909
♪ And it's cool
and the ointment's sweet ♪

39:49.952 --> 39:54.043
♪ For the fire
in your head and feet ♪

