♪ Close your eyes
Close your eyes and relax
Think of nothing tonight ♪

39:59.440 --> 40:04.053
♪ Everything's all right, yes
Everything's all right, yes ♪

40:04.097 --> 40:08.710
♪ Everything's all right, yes
Everything's all right, yes ♪

40:08.754 --> 40:11.670
♪ Everything's all right, yes ♪

40:22.332 --> 40:23.595
Bingo!

40:27.990 --> 40:29.470
Bingo!

40:29.514 --> 40:30.906
Are you there?

40:30.950 --> 40:33.648
Answer me, private,
that's an order!

40:35.476 --> 40:39.132
Eric, what's happening?
Why isn't private Bingo
answering me?

40:40.394 --> 40:41.961
He's dead, Sarge.

40:44.093 --> 40:45.791
Bingo is dead.

40:52.058 --> 40:53.755
[cell phone ringing]

40:55.365 --> 40:56.410
[gasps]

40:56.454 --> 40:58.412
[cell phone ringing continues]

40:58.456 --> 41:00.066
[breathing heavily]

41:10.250 --> 41:11.120
Hello.

41:13.558 --> 41:15.168
Yeah, this is Sergeant Andrews.

41:17.126 --> 41:20.260
I was calling on behalf
of my friend Corporal Jackson.

41:20.303 --> 41:22.828
-[wood creaking]
-[door creaking]

41:26.135 --> 41:26.962
Bingo?

41:27.006 --> 41:29.051
[suspenseful music playing]

41:33.055 --> 41:34.013
[exhales sharply]

41:37.582 --> 41:39.192
I think I might need help, too.
